---
const links = [
  {
    title: '学习',
    items: [
      { label: '教程', href: '/tutorial' },
      { label: '示例', href: '/examples' },
    ],
  },
  {
    title: '资源',
    items: [
      { label: '官方文档（英文/中文）', href: 'https://dora-rs.ai/' },
      { label: 'GitHub 仓库', href: 'https://github.com/dora-rs/dora' },
    ],
  },
  {
    title: '社区',
    items: [
      { label: '中文社区', href: '/community' },
      { label: 'Discord', href: 'https://discord.gg/DXJ6edAtym' },
    ],
  },
];
---

<footer class="border-t border-slate-200/70 bg-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-12">
    <div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-12">
      <div class="md:col-span-5">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <img
            src="/logo.png"
            alt="DORA 中文社区"
            width="36"
            height="36"
            class="size-9 rounded-xl ring-1 ring-slate-200 object-contain bg-white"
            onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling?.classList.remove('hidden');"
          />
          <span class="hidden size-9 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-slate-900 text-sm font-black text-white" aria-hidden="true">D</span>
          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900">DORA 中文社区</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">现代机器人开发框架的中文入口与社区</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-md text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">
          基于 <span class="font-medium text-slate-900">dora-rs</span> 构建，聚焦更好的中文体验：更清晰的入门路径、可复用的示例、以及持续更新的生态信息。
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-md rounded-xl border border-amber-200/80 bg-amber-50/80 px-3 py-2 text-xs leading-5 text-amber-950/90">
          <span class="font-medium">访问提示：</span>
          本站含指向 GitHub、Discord、官方文档等外链；若您所在网络环境访问不稳定，可尝试更换网络或使用镜像/代理后再试。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-8 md:col-span-7 md:grid-cols-3">
        {links.map((group) => (
          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">{group.title}</div>
            <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2">
              {group.items.map((item) => (
                <li>
                  <a
                    href={item.href}
                    class="text-sm text-slate-600 transition hover:text-slate-900"
                    target={item.href.startsWith('http') ? '_blank' : undefined}
                    rel={item.href.startsWith('http') ? 'noreferrer' : undefined}
                  >
                    {item.label}
                  </a>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 space-y-4 border-t border-slate-200 pt-6 text-xs text-slate-500">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 md:flex-row md:flex-wrap md:items-center md:gap-x-6">
        <span>© {new Date().getFullYear()} DORA 中文社区 · doracc.com</span>
        <a
          class="text-slate-600 transition hover:text-[#000063]"
          href="https://beian.miit.gov.cn/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
          >苏ICP备14007268号-19</a
        >
        <a
          class="text-slate-600 transition hover:text-[#000063]"
          href="http://www.beian.gov.cn/portal/registerSystemInfo?recordcode=32050602013520"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
        >
          苏公网安备32050602013520号
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-4 gap-y-2">
        <a class="transition hover:text-slate-900" href="/about">许可与声明</a>
        <a
          class="transition hover:text-slate-900"
          href="https://doracc.com/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
          >旧版站点</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

